EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "HispanicTotVal", 'Population'[HispanicTotVal]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "BlackTotVal", 'Population'[BlackTotVal]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "WhiteTotVal", 'Population'[WhiteTotVal]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "AsianTotVal", 'Population'[AsianTotVal]
)

EVALUATE
  ROW(
  "OtherTotVal", 'Population'[OtherTotVal]
)

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Geo_Dim'[State], "IsGrandTotalRowTotal"),
      ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Population'[Race], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(
      102,
      SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Geo_Dim'[State], [IsGrandTotalRowTotal]),
      [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
      0,
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      1
    )

  VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
    SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Population'[Race], [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal])

  VAR __DS0Secondary = 
    TOPN(102, __DS0SecondaryBase, [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal], 1, 'Population'[Race], 1)

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
      __DS0PrimaryWindowed,
      SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
        __DS0Core,
        "ColumnIndex",
        __DS0Secondary,
        [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal],
        ASC,
        'Population'[Race],
        ASC
      )
    )

EVALUATE
  __DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal], 'Population'[Race]

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  [IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC, 'Geo_Dim'[State], [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
  VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Geo_Dim'[State])),
      NOT('Geo_Dim'[State] IN {BLANK()})
    )

  VAR __DS0Core = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
          'Geo_Dim'[State],
          __DS0FilterTable,
          "BlackTotVal", IGNORE('Population'[BlackTotVal]),
          "HispanicTotVal", IGNORE('Population'[HispanicTotVal]),
          "OtherTotVal", IGNORE('Population'[OtherTotVal]),
          "WhiteTotVal", IGNORE('Population'[WhiteTotVal]),
          "AsianTotVal", IGNORE('Population'[AsianTotVal]),
          "SumPopulation_Value", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value])))
        )
      ),
      NOT(ISBLANK('Geo_Dim'[State]))
    )

  VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(3502, __DS0Core, 'Geo_Dim'[State], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
  'Geo_Dim'[State]

DEFINE
  VAR __SQDS3Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __DataTransformT3 = 
    AI.HighPointLowPointSummary(
      __SQDS3Core,
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", "PrimarySeriesColumnRole"),
        ("[SumPopulation_Value]", "PrimaryValueColumnRole")},
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", BLANK()),
        ("V", "V1"),
        ("V2", "V2"),
        ("V3", "V3"),
        ("V4", "V4"),
        ("V5", "V5"),
        ("TemplateIdColumnRole", "TemplateIdColumnRole")},
      10000
    )

  VAR __SQDS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __DataTransformT0 = 
    AI.AggregateSummary(
      __SQDS0Core,
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", "PrimarySeriesColumnRole"),
        ("[SumPopulation_Value]", "PrimaryValueColumnRole")},
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", BLANK()),
        ("V", "V1"),
        ("V2", "V2"),
        ("V3", "V4"),
        ("V4", "V5"),
        ("V5", "V6"),
        ("V6", "V7"),
        ("V7", "V8"),
        ("V8", "V9"),
        ("V9", "V11"),
        ("V10", "V12"),
        ("V11", "V14"),
        ("V12", "V15"),
        ("V13", "V16"),
        ("V14", "V17"),
        ("V15", "V18"),
        ("TemplateIdColumnRole", "TemplateIdColumnRole")},
      43000,
      "Sum",
      ""
    )

  VAR __SQDS1Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __DataTransformT1 = 
    AI.LargestCategorySummary(
      __SQDS1Core,
      {("[SumPopulation_Value]", "PrimaryValueColumnRole"),
        ("'Geo_Dim'[State]", "PrimarySeriesColumnRole")},
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", BLANK()),
        ("V", "V1"),
        ("V2", "V2"),
        ("V3", "V3"),
        ("TemplateIdColumnRole", "TemplateIdColumnRole")},
      11000
    )

  VAR __SQDS2Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __DataTransformT2 = 
    AI.KPISummary(
      __SQDS2Core,
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", "PrimarySeriesColumnRole"),
        ("[SumPopulation_Value]", "PrimaryValueColumnRole")},
      {("'Geo_Dim'[State]", BLANK()),
        ("V", "V1"),
        ("V2", "V3"),
        ("V3", "V5"),
        ("V4", "V7"),
        ("V5", "V8"),
        ("V6", "V9"),
        ("V7", "V10"),
        ("V8", "V11"),
        ("V9", "V12"),
        ("V10", "V13"),
        ("V11", "V14"),
        ("V12", "V15"),
        ("V13", "V16"),
        ("V14", "V17"),
        ("V15", "V18"),
        ("V16", "V19"),
        ("V17", "V20"),
        ("V18", "V21"),
        ("V19", "V22"),
        ("TemplateIdColumnRole", "TemplateIdColumnRole")},
      56000,
      "",
      "",
      ""
    )

  VAR __FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_0 = 
    GROUPBY(
      __DataTransformT3,
      "MinV", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V]),
      "MinV2", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V2]),
      "MinV5", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V5]),
      "MinV4", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V4]),
      "MinV3", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V3]),
      "MinTemplateIdColumnRole", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TemplateIdColumnRole])
    )

  VAR __FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_1 = 
    GROUPBY(
      __DataTransformT0,
      "MinV6", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V3]),
      "MinV7", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V4]),
      "MinV8", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V5]),
      "MinV9", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V6]),
      "MinV10", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V7]),
      "MinV11", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V8]),
      "MinV12", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V9]),
      "MinV13", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V12]),
      "MinV14", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V13]),
      "MinV15", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V14]),
      "MinTemplateIdColumnRole2", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TemplateIdColumnRole])
    )

  VAR __FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_2 = 
    GROUPBY(
      __DataTransformT1,
      "MinV16", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V]),
      "MinV17", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V2]),
      "MinTemplateIdColumnRole3", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TemplateIdColumnRole])
    )

  VAR __FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_3 = 
    GROUPBY(
      __DataTransformT2,
      "MinV18", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V]),
      "MinV19", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V2]),
      "MinV20", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V5]),
      "MinV21", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V6]),
      "MinV22", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V9]),
      "MinV23", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V10]),
      "MinV24", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V13]),
      "MinV25", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V14]),
      "MinV26", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V15]),
      "MinV27", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V3]),
      "MinV28", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V7]),
      "MinV29", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V11]),
      "MinV30", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V16]),
      "MinV31", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V17]),
      "MinV32", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V4]),
      "MinV33", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V8]),
      "MinV34", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V12]),
      "MinV35", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V18]),
      "MinV36", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [V19]),
      "MinTemplateIdColumnRole4", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [TemplateIdColumnRole])
    )

EVALUATE
  GENERATEALL(
    KEEPFILTERS(ROW(
      "Placeholder", BLANK()
    )),
    GENERATEALL(
      KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_0),
      GENERATEALL(
        KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_1),
        GENERATEALL(
          KEEPFILTERS(__FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_2),
          __FullOuterCrossJoinTableDS0_3
        )
      )
    )
  )

EVALUATE
  ROW(
    "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
  )

EVALUATE
  ROW(
    "SumSurrounding_Pop_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Surrounding Area Population'[Surrounding Pop Value]))
  )

DEFINE
  VAR __SQDS0Core = 
    SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
      'Geo_Dim'[State],
      "SumPopulation_Value", CALCULATE(SUM('Population'[Population Value]))
    )

  VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
    TOPN(10, __SQDS0Core, [SumPopulation_Value], 0)

  VAR __DS0Core =
